Titolo: Company of Heroes: Opposing Fronts

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Company of Heroes: Opposing Fronts (abbreviated CoH:OF) is the stand alone expansion pack to Company of Heroes, a real-time strategy game for computers running the Windows operating system. Opposing Fronts was developed by Canadian-based RTS developer Relic Entertainment, and published by THQ. The game was released on September 25, 2007, in the US and September 28 in Europe. Another standalone expansion to the CoH series, Tales of Valor, was released in April 2009. The game was released as a DLC on IPadOS on April 13, 2020.